% Example queries:
% Find planets with rings:
% ?- planet(Name, _, _, yes).

% Find the diameter of Earth:
% ?- planet(earth, _, Diameter, _).

% List planets in order from the sun:
% ?- planet(Name, Order, _, _), Order =< 4.
